WEBVTT

00:09.000 --> 00:11.640
Katrine Poulsen.
She's Danish Secret Service.

00:12.120 --> 00:12.960
Go back to the office.

00:13.040 --> 00:13.840
You need me there.

00:13.920 --> 00:16.120
Get out or we lose him.
And that's on you.

00:16.200 --> 00:18.520
