15:32.040 --> 15:33.040
Digital voting.

15:33.960 --> 15:36.320
There are people who can manipulate.

15:36.800 --> 15:37.680
Really?

15:38.880 --> 15:40.160
It would save lives.

15:42.200 --> 15:43.880
"It would save lives."

15:50.360 --> 15:53.840
Nicky, I hope that was a joke
because if it's not,

15:54.560 --> 15:56.280
and I'd have to check with Etta, but

15:57.120 --> 15:59.840
I think what you just said
could put you in prison.

16:03.000 --> 16:04.720
Have you stood your agent down?

16:06.520 --> 16:07.320
Not yet.

16:08.200 --> 16:11.680
Look on the positive side.
Now you can concentrate on Redback.

16:17.040 --> 16:20.200
Do you know that the redback
is a type of spider?

16:22.040 --> 16:24.520
You know what the female does
after sex?

16:24.600 --> 16:26.360
Has a fag and a douche.

16:28.000 --> 16:30.080
