-Yeah, I know what she does.

16:36.800 --> 16:37.960
Michael. Hi.

16:39.640 --> 16:40.440
Yes.

16:42.960 --> 16:44.320
Yes. Great. Thanks.

16:47.080 --> 16:48.400
Your boss has overruled you.

16:49.480 --> 16:51.280
-It's on.
-No, I don't believe you.

16:51.360 --> 16:52.240
Call him.

16:56.800 --> 17:01.120
CCTV is disabled inside
and outside The Skanda.

17:01.720 --> 17:04.240
Now, you press this button.

17:05.080 --> 17:07.680
Starts the timer.
That gives them one hour.

17:19.240 --> 17:20.560
From Mr. Laird.

17:23.920 --> 17:25.840
You're like a son to him,
you know that?

17:29.080 --> 17:30.360
He was in the Black Watch?

17:30.440 --> 17:32.080
Belonged to his old fella.

17:34.400 --> 17:35.480
Independence...

17:37.320 --> 17:40.000
People think it's about politics.

17:42.040 --> 17:43.360
It's about blood.

18:02.000 --> 18:02.920
Good luck.

18:34.680 --> 18:36.200
Holly! It's Eva!

18:36.280 --> 18:37.240
Go away.

18:38.840 --> 18:40.040
Open the door!

18:42.520 --> 18:43.880
-Coming!
-Open the door!

18:50.280 --> 18:51.760
You forgot, haven't you?

18:51.840 --> 18:52.880
Forgotten what?

18:52.960 --> 18:55.880
Pub grub, cocktails.
All free. No cash required.

18:55.960 --> 18:59.560
Right. Yeah. 'Cause the honey monster
wants back in your knacks

18:59.640 --> 19:01.480
Don't be horrible. He's a nice guy.

19:02.480 --> 19:03.440
