19:03.880 --> 19:06.520
Oh, come on.
You've not been out for time.

19:06.880 --> 19:08.280
I don't like Danish food.

19:08.360 --> 19:10.440
Fuck's sake, Holly.
Look at the state of you.

19:10.520 --> 19:12.280
Get some fresh air in your lungs.

19:14.320 --> 19:16.240
Doesn't it ever bother you?

19:16.320 --> 19:17.160
What?

19:17.600 --> 19:18.640
You don't fancy the guy.

19:19.400 --> 19:20.880
You're using him for free drinks.

19:21.960 --> 19:23.720
Holly, man, where's this coming from?

19:24.840 --> 19:26.600
I don't like
taking advantage of folk.

19:27.680 --> 19:29.280
Chill out. It cuts both ways.

19:29.360 --> 19:31.040
Yeah? What's he get?

19:32.440 --> 19:35.440
Hope. He can fantasise about,
you know?

19:37.520 --> 19:38.360
What?

19:40.680 --> 19:42.760
I don't know. A nice life.

19:44.400 --> 19:45.640
What if that's all you've got,

19:45.720 --> 19:48.000
