and you're left with nothing?

19:49.640 --> 19:50.440
I think

19:52.200 --> 19:53.120
you need a drink.

19:54.920 --> 19:56.960
I can stretch
to a half-bottle of Bucky

19:57.480 --> 20:01.120
or we can jump on a bus
to a land of free cocktails.

20:03.120 --> 20:04.240
I don't like Bucky.

20:04.320 --> 20:05.600
Ah-ha! Yes!

20:06.040 --> 20:09.280
Come on! Get your face on!
The stage coach leaves at noon.

20:09.720 --> 20:11.840
-Come on. Move!
-Yeah, all right! I'm coming!

20:13.680 --> 20:16.000
Yeah. Beatrice. Good morning.

20:17.040 --> 20:19.520
Levi has some concerns
about the Scottish operation.

20:23.400 --> 20:24.240
The timing's not good.

20:25.240 --> 20:26.160
The timing?

20:26.960 --> 20:28.800
My agent's
on his way there right now.

20:29.320 --> 20:31.200
We can't afford another fuck-up.

20:31.280 --> 20:33.360
Not while we're contending
with Redback.

20:33.440 --> 20:35.520
We've had our funding cut
for the third year in a row.

20:35.600 --> 20:37.480
Look, we're facing multiple threats.

20:37.560 --> 20:40.920
This costs nothing and we take out
one of those threats for good.

20:41.000 --> 20:42.640
We're under scrutiny
from the Home Secretary.

20:42.720 --> 20:45.760
I'm under scrutiny
from the Home Secretary.

20:48.480 --> 20:50.560
All right. Pull the whole thing.
I'll reel Kelvin in.

20:50.640 --> 20:51.880
Laird will know we're on to him,

20:51.960 --> 20:54.720
and the next time he's on our radar
he'll be wearing a suicide vest.

21:02.840 --> 21:04.440
Don't worry about Zac Clark.

21:08.480 --> 21:09.480
No fuck-ups.

21:10.360 --> 21:11.160
Yeah.

21:41.440 --> 21:42.240
Listen, Laird.

21:43.080 --> 21:44.280
Yeah, I've got a problem.

21:45.120 --> 21:46.480
No, I'm outside the pub.

21:47.840 --> 21:50.520
But I had to walk the last half mile.
Something wrong with my car.

21:50.600 --> 21:54.080
<i>Fuck! Get the job done.</i>
<i>I'll get Deke to come for you.</i>

21:54.160 --> 21:54.960
All right.

22:03.200 --> 22:04.800
I made a professional judgement!

22:04.880 --> 22:06.760
Which I disagreed with. Deal with it.

22:06.840 --> 22:09.800
Michael agreed with me
and then you got Daddy to intervene.

22:10.520 --> 22:13.200
Do you ever wonder where you would be
if it wasn't for your father?

22:14.120 --> 22:15.760
-Yes?
-Fucking supply teacher!

22:16.280 --> 22:17.280
I'm about to go in.

22:17.360 --> 22:19.800
<i>-Laird bought it. We're all good.</i>
-OK.

22:19.880 --> 22:22.320
