Wait were we agreed.

22:22.400 --> 22:23.600
All right. I'm on my way.

22:26.400 --> 22:27.240
What is it?

22:28.200 --> 22:29.080
I'm fine.

22:49.040 --> 22:50.040
You're welcome.

22:58.520 --> 23:00.920
No, I don't have a spare.

23:01.880 --> 23:02.920
I know. I...

23:04.120 --> 23:05.160
I know.

23:05.640 --> 23:07.120
I fucked up.

23:26.880 --> 23:29.640
-Katrine? Are you...?
-What?

23:32.560 --> 23:36.120
Can you just go to Scotland and meet
your guy and do your job, OK?

23:46.280 --> 23:50.960
Cheers! Cheers!

23:57.160 --> 23:59.160
Listen very carefully.
This is Amy Brescin.

23:59.640 --> 24:02.080
We've planted a bomb
in The Skanda pub.

24:44.120 --> 24:45.080
Get in!

24:45.760 --> 24:47.400
Kelvin, get fucking in!

24:49.440 --> 24:51.000
No!

25:20.720 --> 25:21.880
Did you lose it?

25:24.840 --> 25:25.720
I don't know.

25:27.560 --> 25:28.360
You should go.

25:28.440 --> 25:30.200
No, I'm gonna take you
to hospital first.

25:30.280 --> 25:33.200
No. I'll be fine on my own. It's OK.

25:34.520 --> 25:35.360
No! Wait!

25:35.440 --> 25:36.840
The bomb went off.

25:39.000 --> 25:40.280
This is on you.

25:42.240 --> 25:43.040
Fuck.

25:56.640 --> 25:59.520
Kelvin, you set the timer?

26:00.240 --> 26:01.280
Yes.

26:02.320 --> 26:03.880
Could anybody have touched it?

26:04.720 --> 26:05.600
No.

26:06.480 --> 26:07.560
Could Deke?

26:12.760 --> 26:13.720
I don't know.

26:16.400 --> 26:18.200
Flat fucking tire, eh?

26:31.120 --> 26:32.840
You're the only one I trust now.

26:44.800 --> 26:45.720
I'm ten years old.

26:50.920 --> 26:52.560
My dad's in a locked ward.

26:56.200 --> 26:57.520
There's blood on his pillow.

27:01.360 --> 27:02.800
His face is half gone.

27:05.760 --> 27:06.840
I made him a promise.

27:09.760 --> 27:11.240
Scotland was gonna be free.

27:16.000 --> 27:17.640
Never gonna happen now, is it?

27:56.920 --> 27:58.000
Thanks.

28:25.440 --> 28:26.680
Have you been inside?

28:27.840 --> 28:30.160
They pulled us.
The building is unsafe.

28:30.680 --> 28:32.920
The fire chief's assessing
when we can go back in.

28:34.680 --> 28:35.520
Was it TNT?

28:36.440 --> 28:38.080
Yes. It was.

28:38.760 --> 28:40.280
Did you pick up anything else?

28:40.760 --> 28:41.560
Sorry?

28:42.120 --> 28:44.680
Did your spectrometer pick up
anything other than TNT?

28:45.480 --> 28:47.800
TNT tends to get the job done.

30:14.840 --> 30:16.240
He's not there?

30:17.120 --> 30:19.240
He's not in hospital.
He hasn't contacted me.

30:20.440 --> 30:22.880
There's no witnesses.
There's no CCTV, in or out.

30:22.960 --> 30:24.400
It was disabled this morning.

30:27.960 --> 30:30.240
The manager and the chef
are among the dead, apparently.

30:33.400 --> 30:34.520
They were Danish.

30:38.240 --> 30:42.600
You go to your meeting place
and, uh, I'll handle it here.

30:51.560 --> 30:52.480
It's OK.

30:52.560 --> 30:53.760
Just hold it together, all right?

30:53.840 --> 30:54.840
It's OK.

30:56.040 --> 30:57.320
Hey. Wait.

30:58.120 --> 31:00.600
-Holly.
-What happened? We just got here.

31:00.680 --> 31:03.400
I don't have any details.
What are you doing here?

31:03.480 --> 31:05.040
My friend's ex works there.

31:05.120 --> 31:06.600
I can't tell you anything.

31:09.280 --> 31:10.520
What's your friend's name?

31:11.120 --> 31:12.160
Niels...

31:12.640 --> 31:15.000
Niels Vilfort. He's the chef.

31:17.280 --> 31:20.640
Well, I've got Holly's number,
so if I hear anything, I'll call you.

31:21.080 --> 31:22.600
What if I need to call you?

31:22.680 --> 31:24.000
I'll send you my number.

31:30.120 --> 31:31.040
God.

32:01.280 --> 32:02.440
<i>Police have confirmed</i>

32:02.520 --> 32:05.600
<i>that the bomb blast at The Skanda pub</i>
<i>in the Scottish Borders</i>

32:05.680 --> 32:09.040
<i>has left a number of people suffering</i>
<i>life-changing injuries</i>

32:09.120 --> 32:11.000
<i>and multiple fatalities.</i>

32:11.080 --> 32:14.520
<i>But so far the exact death toll</i>
<i>is yet to be confirmed.</i>

32:15.400 --> 32:17.120
<i>The bomb is thought to be the work</i>

32:17.200 --> 32:19.800
<i>of the Scottish</i>
<i>nationalist terrorist organisation,</i>

32:19.880 --> 32:21.160
<i>Amy Brescin.</i>

32:21.880 --> 32:24.520
<i>A member of the group</i>
<i>called the police security number</i>

32:24.600 --> 32:28.000
<i>claiming responsibility</i>
<i>just seconds before the blast.</i>

32:29.040 --> 32:32.240
<i>This group</i>
<i>has been linked with attacks...</i>

32:33.360 --> 32:34.960
Right, well, I'll put a fire on.

32:56.320 --> 32:57.440
No!

33:00.760 --> 33:01.960
You fucker!

33:12.680 --> 33:15.240
-Who are you fucking working for?
-I don't know.

33:15.320 --> 33:17.080
Who are you fucking working for?

33:33.600 --> 33:35.040
I trusted you!

33:35.120 --> 33:37.080
I fucking trusted you!

33:42.080 --> 33:44.080
I fucking trusted you!

33:51.400 --> 33:52.440
Little brat!

34:00.560 --> 34:01.600
Do it.

34:02.320 --> 34:03.400
Do it, then!

34:04.800 --> 34:05.800
Do it!

34:34.040 --> 34:36.280
You all right?
It's OK, Kelvin. It's OK.

34:37.280 --> 34:38.080
You all right?

34:38.160 --> 34:39.960
Talk to me. It's all right.

34:53.240 --> 34:54.080
Hey.

34:54.520 --> 34:55.560
Hi.

34:55.640 --> 34:56.800
Something's odd?

34:57.760 --> 34:59.320
Yes. Odd.

35:00.360 --> 35:02.960
I found it in the gents.
It's the detonator.

35:03.440 --> 35:04.880
They used an AAL.

35:06.120 --> 35:08.840
It's the rubber seal
that holds the shot tube in place.

35:09.600 --> 35:11.480
So... So what's odd?

35:14.000 --> 35:15.120
Why is there two?

35:24.360 --> 35:25.160
Look,

35:26.040 --> 35:27.840
you have to talk to me, Kelvin.

35:27.920 --> 35:29.760
OK? I need to know what happened.

35:31.680 --> 35:32.520
No.

35:33.600 --> 35:35.960
No. You can have that
when you tell me that went wrong.

35:36.720 --> 35:38.240
I don't know what went wrong.

35:39.520 --> 35:41.360
I did what I was supposed to do.

35:41.440 --> 35:44.120
You couldn't have done!
Eleven people died!

35:45.920 --> 35:47.440
Somebody sabotaged it.

35:48.880 --> 35:50.120
Who could that have been?

35:50.200 --> 35:51.200
Too many knew.

35:51.280 --> 35:52.080
Who?

35:52.520 --> 35:55.360
That Danish bint, huh?
Her department.

35:56.200 --> 35:57.920
How many in your office knew?

35:58.000 --> 35:59.400
You used me!

35:59.480 --> 36:01.680
Don't blame the people I work with
for your screw-up!

36:02.520 --> 36:03.480
I...

36:07.560 --> 36:09.800
I killed 'em. Fuck.

36:11.000 --> 36:12.520
I killed all those people.

36:14.800 --> 36:16.200
There was a girl in there.

36:17.080 --> 36:18.200
And she smiled.

36:19.400 --> 36:20.800
She smiled at me.

36:25.640 --> 36:26.440
Come on.

36:27.640 --> 36:28.880
It's not your fault, Kelvin.

36:28.960 --> 36:30.240
I know. I didn't...

36:31.400 --> 36:32.760
I didn't mean to...

36:32.840 --> 36:34.840
I didn't... I didn't mean...

36:35.440 --> 36:36.480
What are you doing?

36:37.480 --> 36:39.520
Kelvin, get off of me.
Get off. What are you doing?

36:39.600 --> 36:40.400
Please help.

36:40.480 --> 36:41.520
What are you doing?

36:41.600 --> 36:43.600
-Please help me.
-Get off me. Kelvin!

36:43.680 --> 36:45.000
Help me.

36:48.200 --> 36:50.640
Don't ever do that to me ever again!

36:52.960 --> 36:54.880
I'm sorry. I'm sorry.

37:02.400 --> 37:03.240
Wait.

37:04.960 --> 37:05.760
No!

37:06.440 --> 37:07.320
No!

37:14.000 --> 37:17.080
The guy I talked to thinks
they used two detonators.

37:19.600 --> 37:22.760
Most of the evidence has been
formerly given to us to look at.

37:23.240 --> 37:25.920
And what when we can see
from what we have in front of us...

37:26.600 --> 37:28.200
Who benefits from this?

37:28.600 --> 37:30.160
The British government.

37:31.640 --> 37:32.920
What can I do?

37:36.000 --> 37:37.160
You decide.

37:39.760 --> 37:42.440
Now, Kelvin, the ambulance
will be here in a minute.

37:45.360 --> 37:46.960
This is on Laird.

37:47.720 --> 37:48.880
All right? Nobody else.

37:50.360 --> 37:52.600
You don't take the blame
anymore, Kelvin.

37:52.680 --> 37:53.480
Do you hear me?

37:55.160 --> 37:56.800
All right? You don't take the blame.

38:00.160 --> 38:03.200
<i>And as the standard death roll</i>
<i>rises to 11,</i>

38:03.280 --> 38:06.240
<i>we ask what does that mean</i>
<i>for Scottish independence?</i>

38:07.160 --> 38:09.360
I think we know what it means
for Scottish independence.

38:10.320 --> 38:12.720
Don't let anyone outside this room
hear you say that.

38:16.120 --> 38:17.280
Our official line,

38:18.320 --> 38:20.240
this is an absolute tragedy.

38:21.040 --> 38:22.960
We don't want it
to affect the way people vote.

38:24.560 --> 38:25.360
Right.

38:27.200 --> 38:28.200
The funerals.

38:29.440 --> 38:32.320
-I think we should consider...
-Do not say the optics.

38:32.880 --> 38:35.640
Should you attend the funerals?
That's all I'm asking.

38:36.320 --> 38:38.280
Or is it not better
we organise a service?

38:38.360 --> 38:39.880
Involve all the first responders.

38:39.960 --> 38:41.640
I'm going to the funerals.

38:42.640 --> 38:43.680
All of them.

38:43.760 --> 38:45.400
-The ones in Denmark?
-All of them.

38:45.480 --> 38:48.760
It'll be spun. Made to look
like it's about political capital.

38:48.840 --> 38:51.680
So, we put a poll in the field.
Somebody we trust.

38:51.760 --> 38:53.240
I don't need a bloody poll!

38:54.320 --> 38:56.400
I'm going
because it's the right thing to do.

39:00.800 --> 39:01.640
Well...

39:03.280 --> 39:05.560
I'm guessing you flirted an idea.

39:05.640 --> 39:06.640
Oh, he loved it.

39:07.120 --> 39:08.400
Said I could go to prison.

39:08.480 --> 39:09.280
No?

39:10.840 --> 39:13.160
Another day and there would've been
no need to mention it.

39:14.840 --> 39:17.920
Well, you always find
the silver lining.

39:18.800 --> 39:20.000
That's why you hired me.

39:22.560 --> 39:25.000
Kelvin's been sent
to Chatham Military Hospital. OK?

39:25.080 --> 39:26.680
I want an armed guard on the door

39:26.760 --> 39:28.600
and I want
round-the-clock suicide watch.

39:28.680 --> 39:31.040
And what am I supposed to tell
the Home Secretary?

39:31.560 --> 39:33.480
Tell him he'll have the answers
when we have them.

39:33.560 --> 39:36.520
And what about Laird? This whole
thing was about bringing him in.

39:36.600 --> 39:37.760
Yeah. I don't know.

39:37.840 --> 39:40.560
This is an unmitigated fuck-up,
Beatrice!

39:40.640 --> 39:41.840
This could bring us all down.

39:41.920 --> 39:43.080
I'm gonna fix it, all right?

39:43.160 --> 39:45.080
I said I'll fix it,
and that's what I'm gonna do.

39:45.880 --> 39:47.040
Fuck!

40:22.320 --> 40:23.560
Morning.

40:23.640 --> 40:24.480
Good morning.

40:25.200 --> 40:27.240
Are you all done in Scotland?

40:27.320 --> 40:29.320
Yeah. Finished last night.

40:29.880 --> 40:30.800
Yeah.

40:33.560 --> 40:35.640
What I told you yesterday, I...

40:36.800 --> 40:39.000
I... I made a mistake.

40:40.400 --> 40:42.440
I was wrong
about there being two seals.

40:44.360 --> 40:45.320
OK.

40:45.400 --> 40:46.360
The...

40:47.520 --> 40:49.200
The force of the blast

40:49.800 --> 40:51.280
made it split along the seam.

41:00.480 --> 41:01.800
Better to know the truth.

41:04.280 --> 41:05.160
Sure.

41:07.800 --> 41:08.720
Have a good day.

41:09.240 --> 41:10.400
Yeah, you too.

41:20.800 --> 41:21.720
I get it. I get it.

41:23.240 --> 41:24.120
What happened?

41:25.800 --> 41:27.320
What do you mean what happened?

41:27.880 --> 41:28.680
To your head?

41:29.440 --> 41:30.440
Oh. Yeah.

41:31.560 --> 41:32.600
It was nothing.

41:33.400 --> 41:35.160
The baby's fine, by the way.

41:36.520 --> 41:37.640
OK, yeah.

41:42.800 --> 41:45.080
Right. Result.

41:45.160 --> 41:47.960
Home Secretary's guaranteed
they'll be no enquiry.

41:48.040 --> 41:50.480
The public have a madman
with a history of violence

41:50.560 --> 41:52.400
and terrorist
still under lock and key.

41:52.480 --> 41:54.560
Motive evidence. No CCTV.

41:54.640 --> 41:58.120
From now on, we can sign this
to history and move on.

41:59.160 --> 42:00.280
No more diversions.

42:00.360 --> 42:06.400
Tattoo Redback on your eyeballs!

42:07.360 --> 42:11.520
From now on, it's all you're
gonna see until we have cracked it,

42:11.600 --> 42:15.320
killed it
and pissed merrily on its corpse.

43:24.320 --> 43:26.880
Evil English bastards.

43:29.000 --> 43:32.280
Eleven dead
'cause you need our fucking oil.

43:32.360 --> 43:33.760
I know you need to believe that,

43:33.840 --> 43:36.080
but the truth
is one of our agents made a mistake.

43:36.160 --> 43:37.120
No.

43:38.320 --> 43:40.040
Your agent was EOD.

43:41.440 --> 43:43.240
That was sabotage.

43:44.600 --> 43:49.240
And you are some other bastard.

43:52.400 --> 43:53.920
That was no mistake.

43:58.800 --> 44:00.320
You don't like that, do you?

44:07.920 --> 44:09.640
Can't be having me in court.

44:10.400 --> 44:13.280
You wanna play the grownups' games,
you need to know the rules.

44:15.480 --> 44:16.840
I know the rules.

44:19.400 --> 44:20.920
I know who betrayed me.

44:25.680 --> 44:26.920
Who betrayed you?

45:00.800 --> 45:02.840
We've been
over Kutiev's online comms.

45:02.920 --> 45:04.400
Maybe he was bluffing about Redback.

45:04.480 --> 45:06.200
Then why did Adamov kill him?

45:06.280 --> 45:09.720
The coroner forged the report
from the bombing.

45:09.800 --> 45:12.560
Our intel
has Torben Jensen in London.

45:12.640 --> 45:14.920
He's in contact
with the bias linked to Daesh.

45:15.560 --> 45:17.600
You only care about yourself!

45:17.680 --> 45:19.800
I sacrificed every principle I have
to protect you,

45:19.880 --> 45:20.880
so don't fucking go there!

45:20.960 --> 45:23.400
I know about tweaking
the referendum results.

45:23.480 --> 45:24.920
You got it all wrong.

45:25.000 --> 45:26.400
It was a joke.

45:26.480 --> 45:30.600
Laird isn't the man I saw
and you can't make me say he is!

45:30.680 --> 45:34.760
I just had a message from Holly.
Someone she knows died in that bomb.

45:34.840 --> 45:36.440
Katrine said you know him.

45:36.520 --> 45:38.800
When I say no diversions,
I mean no diversions.

45:38.880 --> 45:41.320
Whoa, whoa! Redback? Who is it?

45:41.400 --> 45:44.720
This is an indication
that Redback is an individual.

45:44.800 --> 45:47.600
I have information
you're going to be interested in.

45:48.120 --> 45:49.160
Who is Redback?

45:50.280 --> 45:52.160
You know I can't allow that
to happen.

45:54.560 --> 45:56.760
